{{root|en|ine-pro|*dewk-}}
From {{der|en|la|abductiō|t=robbing; abduction}}, from {{m|la|abdūcō|t=take or lead away}}, from {{m|la|ab|t=away}} + {{m|la|dūcō|t=to lead}}<ref>{{R:CDOE|page=2}}</ref>. Equivalent to {{suffix|en|abduct|ion}}.
